OL,7,B"I don't get much exercise, but I do   
OL,8,Blike dancing. I'll bop round my front  
OL,9,Broom, even to my own records!" says    
OL,10,Bchart-topping Olive singerERuth-Ann.   
OL,12,BTina Moore, currently in the charts    
OL,13,BwithENever Gonna Let You Go,Bsays: "I  
OL,14,Blove dancing. It clears your mind and  
OL,15,Bdoes your body the world of good."     
OL,17,BTina used to be a professional dancer  
OL,18,Bin New York before she scaled the dizzy
OL,19,Bheights of pop stardom.                
